The summer season is on the peak, so the charming Barbie has decided to enjoy her vacation on the beach. She is very excited to go outside and enjoy the cool environment near the sea. But, the pretty girl needs your help to complete her beach vacation. Do you guide her to make all the arrangements she needs to do before the departure? Join Barbie Superhero Beach Vacation game and be prepared to help her pick up some suitable and wonderful bikini to make her look more stunning!

Apart from dressing her up, you have to take care of various other things to give her a memorable trip on the beach. There are three unique levels to deal with in this brand new dressing game for girls. Decorate the car of her beloved Barbie with the help of some images! Help the princess to spot the appropriate road so that she can start her van in the second level. When you will arrive at the beach, make sure to dress her up with a beautiful swimsuit and match it up with a fancy sunglass in the third level. Do not forget to give a cup of refreshing fruit to your girl. 

Try to do your best to make her weekend so interesting and engaging and allow the girl to beat the boredom with ease in this html5 doll dress up game! Mix and match as many items as you can to dress her up in the perfect bikini style! Princess has a full on your ultimate fashion abilities, so do your best to make her look pretty attractive. Create a special swimsuit for your beloved princess in just a few clicks! Play your favorite girls games as many times as you want without download!
